{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"74e9f7250e","title":"给冯元春的信","origin":"《四川省右派言论选集》（内部文件，只供领导同志参考，请勿外传和翻印），中共四川省委宣传部办公室编，1957年7月20日。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"ea47aba28a","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":19,"articleId":"74e9f7250e"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"a185c9b36c","name":"四川"},{"id":"d14cb1e7e0","name":"史克芬"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"bcf2cd8d54","type":"title","text":"给冯元春的信","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"74e9f7250e"},{"id":"9be2027322","type":"authors","text":"四川史克芬","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"74e9f7250e"},{"id":"686f70c0eb","type":"subtitle","text":"铁路二局史克芬给冯元春的信","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"74e9f7250e"},{"id":"f5460574a9","type":"subtitle","text":"(据说“史克芬”是铁路二局一个党员的化名)","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"74e9f7250e"},{"id":"61674c76c1","type":"appellation","text":"冯元春同志：","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"74e9f7250e"},{"id":"b36f5a1190","type":"paragraph","text":"我昨天听了你的演讲后，我很欣喜和赞叹，对于这种新型的创举，万不料被你早鸣，我向你表示敬仰。但我觉得你的论述内容还不够充实，这方面的材料我搜的不少，对这个问题，我前几天也有所思豫，总是虑而不敢易举。我愿与你合作研究，把我们共同论点求得更具体更有说服力，如何，千急覆告。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"74e9f7250e"},{"id":"8782d3ccb1","type":"paragraph","text":"(最好约定时间地点面谈为宜，如何？)","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"74e9f7250e"},{"id":"79328aeec4","type":"appellation","text":"革命敬礼","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"74e9f7250e"},{"id":"41f5cd1931","type":"paragraph","text":" 铁路二局史克芬上57.6.19回信请写：本市西门外理学路铁路二局收发室转史克芬收","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"74e9f7250e"}],"page":{"id":"445b001319","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"74e9f7250e","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}